Menu:         View|Contents of|8K BASIC variables
Type:         Command
Shortcut:     Alt,V,F,B (IBM-PC)
CLI Argument: n/a
Debugger:     VIEW BASIC
ARexx:        DEBUGGER VIEW BASIC
Default:      n/a
Hosts:        Both
